Table 3. Comparison of the Calculated (ΔE<sub>f,rel</sub>) and Experimental (ΔH<sub>f,rel</sub>) Enthalpies of Formation of Herein Explored ZIFs Relative to ZIF-8

| framework | ΔH<sub>f,rel</sub> (kJ·mol<sup>–1</sup>) (experimental) | ΔE<sub>f,rel</sub> (kJ·mol<sup>–1</sup>) (calculated) |
|-----------|------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| Zn(MeIm)<sub>2</sub> | 0.0 | 0.0 |
| Zn(VIm)<sub>2</sub> | 3.87 ± 1.45 | 1.06 |
| Zn(ClIm)<sub>2</sub> | 0.97 ± 1.15 | –2.74 |
| Zn(IIm)<sub>2</sub> | 14.01 ± 1.23 | 8.10 |
| Zn(CF<sub>3</sub>Im)<sub>2</sub> | 16.63 ± 1.10 | 14.54 |
| Zn(CHOIm)<sub>2</sub> | 57.10 ± 1.39 | 50.21 |
